<function>

access:  static public

name: factory

param: string, $class

param: array, $config, NULL

return: object

</function>

Convenience method to instantiate and configure an object.

* Parameters:

 * string //$class//: The class name.

 * array //$config//: Additional configuration array for the class.

* Returns object: A new instance of the requested class.

